---
title: Easy Chermoula Beef Rump & Veggie Coucous with Garlic Dip
description: Who doesn’t like a bit of char on their beef? This one gets a generous coating of our punchy chermoula spice blend before it crisps up in the pan until golden. Finish it off in the oven so you have the most succulent result that pairs beautifully with our veggie-packed couscous.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/664eee630ab4934df86335c1-be305728.jpeg
